            <title>[SOLR-226] support dynamic fields as copyField destination</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-226</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I&apos;d like to use a dynamic field as the destination of a copyField:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Given:&lt;br/&gt;
  &amp;lt;field name=&quot;tag_*&quot;   type=&quot;string&quot; ... /&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
  &amp;lt;field name=&quot;text_*&quot;  type=&quot;text&quot;   ... /&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I want:&lt;br/&gt;
  &amp;lt;copyField source=&quot;tag_&lt;b&gt;&quot; dest=&quot;text_&lt;/b&gt;&quot; /&amp;gt; &lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;For background see:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.nabble.com/copyField-to-a-dynamic-field-tf2300115.html#a6419101&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://www.nabble.com/copyField-to-a-dynamic-field-tf2300115.html#a6419101&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

